		<td><b>HIROM game on a LOROM board ?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It seems like this may be possible through address remapping, but I haven't found anything that shows or explains how. <br /><br />I've successfully made a few LOROM dev carts, I'm now looking to make a HIROM cart. I need to use 2x27c801 eproms so I figure if I can use a dual maskrom LOROM board then its a bit less work then using a single maskrom HIROM board and wiring in 2x27c801 eproms to a single maskrom socket + a *39 address mapper.<br /><br />Any help or suggestion would be greatly appreciated.<br /><br />Thank you.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

